Package hu.sztaki.sztakipediaparser.wiki.parser

Provides the JavaCC source file JavaCCWikiParser.jj, stores the output classes of the JavaCC generated parser and has some utility classes.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IWikiParser Interface for the parser.
JavaCCWikiParserConstants Token literal values and constants.
 

Class Summary
JavaCCWikiParser Wiki parser generated by JavaCC.
JavaCCWikiParserTokenManager Token Manager.
Parser Main class of the parser.
SimpleCharStream An implementation of interface CharStream, where the stream is assumed to contain only ASCII characters (without unicode processing).
Splitter Splits a string using regex delimiters, optionally keeping the delimiters.
Token Describes the input token stream.
 

Exception Summary
ParseException This exception is thrown when parse errors are encountered.
 

Error Summary
TokenMgrError Token Manager Error.
 

Package hu.sztaki.sztakipediaparser.wiki.parser Description

Provides the JavaCC source file JavaCCWikiParser.jj, stores the output classes of the JavaCC generated parser and has some utility classes. Also provides the Parser class which is the entry point of the parser.
